attachments.text:
*Changes*

• Tests are now more reliable
• Remove all explicit mentions and standardize host url accross all tests
• Refactored code for less repetitions
• Enable 2 retry attempts on fail
• Add script to run all tests in visual mode

*Cypress Commands*  
_To run all tests in headless mode_  
`yarn cypress:run`  
_To run all tests visually in headed mode_  
`yarn cypress:run:gui`  
_To debug tests_  
`yarn cypress:open`

*Note*

• The test corresponding with _user roles_ is disabled until the back-end issue with login attempts is resolved, a separate issue will be taken later.
